. Feature your favorite homepage content in either a grid or a slider. Use the three widget areas to customize your website, and change your content\'s layout with a full-width page template and a contributor page to show off your authors. Creating a magazine website with WordPress has never been easier.\";s:6:\"Author\";s:18:\"the WordPress team\";s:9:\"AuthorURI\";s:22:\"https://wordpress.org/\";s:7:\"Version\";s:3:\"1.9\";s:8:\"Template\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"Status\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"Tags\";s:317:\"blog, news, two-columns, three-columns, left-sidebar, right-sidebar, custom-background, custom-header, custom-menu, editor-style, featured-images, flexible-header, footer-widgets, full-width-template, microformats, post-formats, rtl-language-support, sticky-post, theme-options, translation-ready, accessibility-ready\";s:10:\"TextDomain\";s:14:\"twentyfourteen\";s:10:\"DomainPath\";s:0:\"\";}s:27:\"\0WP_Theme\0headers_sanitized\";N;s:25:\"\0WP_Theme\0name_translated\";N;s:16:\"\0WP_Theme\0errors\";N;s:20:\"\0WP_Theme\0stylesheet\";s:14:\"twentyfourteen\";s:18:\"\0WP_Theme\0template\";s:14:\"twentyfourteen\";s:16:\"\0WP_Theme\0parent\";N;s:24:\"\0WP_Theme\0theme_root_uri\";N;s:27:\"\0WP_Theme\0textdomain_loaded\";N;s:20:\"\0WP_Theme\0cache_hash\";s:32:\"0c7e8dfcb7f6bfe62746c98dd0d725eb\";}s:15:\"twentyseventeen\";O:8:\"WP_Theme\":12:{s:6:\"update\";b:0;s:20:\"\0WP_Theme\0theme_root\";s:22:\"/app/wp-content/themes\";s:17:\"\0WP_Theme\0headers\";a:11:{s:4:\"Name\";s:16:\"Twenty Seventeen\";s:8:\"ThemeURI\";s:45:\"https://wordpress.org/themes/twentyseventeen/\";s:11:\"Description\";s:450:\"Twenty Seventeen brings your site to life with header video and immersive featured images. With a focus on business sites, it features multiple sections on the front page as well as widgets, navigation and social menus, a logo, and more. Personalize its asymmetrical grid with a custom color scheme and showcase your multimedia content with post formats. Our default theme for 2017 works great in many languages, for any abilities, and on any device.\";s:6:\"Author\";s:18:\"the WordPress team\";s:9:\"AuthorURI\";s:22:\"https://wordpress.org/\";s:7:\"Version\";s:3:\"1.1\";s:8:\"Template\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"Status\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"Tags\";s:281:\"one-column, two-columns, right-sidebar, flexible-header, accessibility-ready, custom-colors, custom-header, custom-menu, custom-logo, editor-style, featured-images, footer-widgets, post-formats, rtl-language-support, sticky-post, theme-options, threaded-comments, translation-ready\";s:10:\"TextDomain\";s:15:\"twentyseventeen\";s:10:\"DomainPath\";s:0:\"\";}s:27:\"\0WP_Theme\0headers_sanitized\";N;s:25:\"\0WP_Theme\0name_translated\";N;s:16:\"\0WP_Theme\0errors\";N;s:20:\"\0WP_Theme\0stylesheet\";s:15:\"twentyseventeen\";s:18:\"\0WP_Theme\0template\";s:15:\"twentyseventeen\";s:16:\"\0WP_Theme\0parent\";N;s:24:\"\0WP_Theme\0theme_root_uri\";N;s:27:\"\0WP_Theme\0textdomain_loaded\";N;s:20:\"\0WP_Theme\0cache_hash\";s:32:\"adb0565ed2d14137d7cced3fac2617a9\";}s:13:\"twentysixteen\";O:8:\"WP_Theme\":12:{s:6:\"update\";b:0;s:20:\"\0WP_Theme\0theme_root\";s:22:\"/app/wp-content/themes\";s:17:\"\0WP_Theme\0headers\";a:11:{s:4:\"Name\";s:14:\"Twenty Sixteen\";s:8:\"ThemeURI\";s:43:\"https://wordpress.org/themes/twentysixteen/\";s:11:\"Description\";s:402:\"Twenty Sixteen is a modernized take on an ever-popular WordPress layout  the horizontal masthead with an optional right sidebar that works perfectly for blogs and websites. It has custom color options with beautiful default color schemes, a harmonious fluid grid using a mobile-first approach, and impeccable polish in every detail. Twenty Sixteen will make your WordPress look beautiful everywhere.\";s:6:\"Author\";s:18:\"the WordPress team\";s:9:\"AuthorURI\";s:22:\"https://wordpress.org/\";s:7:\"Version\";s:3:\"1.3\";s:8:\"Template\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"Status\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"Tags\";s:276:\"one-column, two-columns, right-sidebar, accessibility-ready, custom-background, custom-colors, c